GASC is an NFT collection of 10,000 provably unique, hand-drawn, pixel art Aliens programmatically generated with over 300+ attributes and traits.

Each Alien is stored on the Ethereum blockchain as an ERC-721 token and hosted on IPFS.

Owning an Alien will act as a membership card granting you exclusive access to our Social Club– giving you opportunities for giveaways, raffles, airdrops and extra content.
